description: This easy roast pumpkin soup recipe is on the table in just 20 minutes. With only five ingredients, it's the ultimate midweek dinner.
keywords: Easy Roasted Pumpkin & Sweet Potato Soup
name: Easy Roasted Pumpkin & Sweet Potato Soup Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 kg Woolworths diced pumpkin & sweet potato
400 ml canned Macro Organic coconut milk

recipeInstructions.text: Ladle soup among bowls. Drizzle with remaining coconut milk and swirl to create a marble effect. Top with chopped coriander leaves and serve.
